{"model": "doubao-seed-2-0-pro-260215", "input": [{"type": "message", "role": "user", "content": [{"type": "input_video", "file_id": "file-20260610003049-jzgnv"}, {"type": "input_text", "text": "你是短视频结构分析师。分析这个视频的创作结构，而不是复述剧情。\n把视频拆成若干可迁移的片段。start_time 和 end_time 使用秒，统一保留小数点后一位。\ndescription 写清画面、动作、节奏作用和可迁移的剪辑意图，如果出现字幕内容请描述它所在的位置。你需要尽可能多地分段，颗粒度细化一些。"}]}], "text": {"format": {"type": "json_schema", "name": "video_ir", "strict": true, "schema": {"type": "object", "properties": {"parts": {"type": "array", "items": {"type": "object", "properties": {"start_time": {"type": "number", "description": "片段开始时间，单位秒，保留小数点后一位。"}, "end_time": {"type": "number", "description": "片段结束时间，单位秒，保留小数点后一位。"}, "description": {"type": "string", "description": "片段内容和可迁移作用。"}}, "required": ["start_time", "end_time", "description"], "additionalProperties": false}, "description": "视频片段列表。"}}, "required": ["parts"], "additionalProperties": false}}}}